<surveypage SSS1>
/ caption = "Each of the items below contains two choices, A and B.  Please click the letter of the choice which most describes your likes or the way you feel.  In some cases you may find items in which both choices describe your likes or feelings.  Please choose the one which better describes your likes or feelings.  In some cases you may find items in which you do not like either choice.  In these cases mark the choice you dislike least.  Do not leave any items blank.

It is important you respond to all items with only one choice, A or B.  We are interested only in your likes or feelings, not in how others feel about these things or how one is supposed to feel.  There are not right or wrong answers as in other kinds of tests.  Be frank and give your honest appraisal of yourself.
"
/ questions = [1 = q1R_DIS, q2_BOR]
</surveypage>


